### ANALYST REQUESTS

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@analystToken = PASTE_REAL_ANALYST_TOKEN_HERE
@userId = USER_ID_HERE
@recordId = FINANCIAL_RECORD_ID_HERE

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Analyst Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Get Own User By Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Create Financial Record
POST {{baseUrl}}/financial-records
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 875,
  "type": "expense",
  "category": "Software",
  "date": "2026-04-06",
  "notes": "License renewal",
  "userId": "{{userId}}"
}

###

### Get Financial Records
GET {{baseUrl}}/financial-records
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Filter Financial Records
GET {{baseUrl}}/financial-records?type=expense&category=Software&dateFrom=2026-01-01&dateTo=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Get Financial Record By Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/financial-records/{{recordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Update Financial Record
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/financial-records/{{recordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Updated by analyst"
}

###

### Dashboard Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Weekly Dashboard Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary?dateFrom=2026-01-01&dateTo=2026-04-30&period=weekly
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}
